---
---
<section class="hiw" id="how-it-works">
  <div class="hiw-inner">
    <div class="hiw-header">
      <h2 class="display-headline hiw-headline reveal">
        How This Workshop Will Arm You With the Right<br />
        Knowledge and Tools to Build<br />
        <em>Your 6-Figure FBA Business.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-columns reveal">

      <!-- Left: what you get -->
      <div class="hiw-col hiw-col--yes">
        <div class="hiw-item">
          <span class="hiw-icon hiw-icon--yes"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i></span>
          <p><strong>6 Intensive Sessions:</strong> This Bootcamp is divided into 6 Sessions to teach you everything you need to run a successful FBA business from A to Z along with winning Strategies and methods that have been taught to my FBA students in my online Academy to build their 6 figure businesses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-item">
          <span class="hiw-icon hiw-icon--yes"><i class="fa-solid fa-check"></i></span>
          <p><strong>90 Days Aftercare:</strong> After the bootcamp, you're given 90 days access to a private group membership where you'll receive further support and assistance and 2 weekly coaching calls to answer all your questions and help you in your FBA journey.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: what this isn't -->
      <div class="hiw-col hiw-col--no">
        <p class="hiw-col-intro">And No, this isn't like what other gurus sell you:</p>
        <div class="hiw-item">
          <span class="hiw-icon hiw-icon--no"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>
          <p><strong>Not just a "Class":</strong> We teach, build and implement in front of you to make sure you walk away knowing how to build a successful and profitable FBA business from scratch without any confusion or procrastinations.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="hiw-item">
          <span class="hiw-icon hiw-icon--no"><i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i></span>
          <p><strong>Unlike Any Free Resource:</strong> Unlike anything you can find in a pricey online course, YouTube tutorials or some gurus, what we teach is high-valuable knowledge based on my expertise as an FBA seller who generated 5M in revenue. We teach the real thing so we know our stuff!</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <div class="hiw-cta-block reveal">
      <p class="hiw-urgency">
        <span class="hiw-urgency-dot"></span>
        Hurry up before all seats are taken — Doors close <strong>March 1st!</strong>
      </p>
      <a href="#offer" class="btn-primary hiw-btn">Reserve My Seat Now</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hiw {
    background: var(--color-dark-brown);
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hiw-inner {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .hiw-header {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 72px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hiw-headline {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 56px);
    color: #1A1A1A;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .hiw-headline em {
    color: #fff;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  /* ── Columns ── */
  .hiw-columns {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .hiw-col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .hiw-col--yes { }
  .hiw-col--no  { }

  .hiw-col-intro {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: #fff;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
    padding: 20px 32px;
    background: #2d1f0d;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
  }

  .hiw-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 18px;
    padding: 28px 32px;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .hiw-col--yes .hiw-item { background: #1A1A1A; }
  .hiw-col--no  .hiw-item { background: #2d1f0d; }

  .hiw-icon {
    font-size: 13px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }

  .hiw-icon--yes { color: #e07c12; }
  .hiw-icon--no  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.25); }

  .hiw-item p {
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    font-size: 15.5px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .hiw-col--yes .hiw-item p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); }
  .hiw-col--no  .hiw-item p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75); }

  .hiw-col--yes .hiw-item p strong { color: #fff; font-weight: 700; }
  .hiw-col--no  .hiw-item p strong { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.95); font-weight: 700; }

  /* ── CTA ── */
  .hiw-cta-block {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .hiw-urgency {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #1A1A1A;
  }

  .hiw-urgency strong { color: #1A1A1A; font-weight: 700; }

  .hiw-urgency-dot {
    width: 6px;
    height: 6px;
    background: #1A1A1A;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    animation: pulse-dot 1.8s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse-dot {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50%       { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.7); }
  }

  .hiw-btn {
    background: #1A1A1A;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .hiw-btn:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(26,26,26,0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hiw { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .hiw-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .hiw-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .hiw-columns { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hiw-item { padding: 22px 24px; }
    .hiw-col-intro { padding: 18px 24px; }
  }
</style>

<script>
  import { gsap } from 'gsap';
  import { ScrollTrigger } from 'gsap/ScrollTrigger';
  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  gsap.fromTo('#how-it-works .hiw-item',
    { opacity: 0, y: 20 },
    {
      opacity: 1, y: 0,
      duration: 0.6,
      stagger: 0.1,
      ease: 'power2.out',
      scrollTrigger: { trigger: '#how-it-works .hiw-columns', start: 'top 80%' }
    }
  );
</script>
